<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4586659>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Text-fig. 8. Cyrtograptus hemmanni BOUČEK, 1934 from the upper lundgreni Biozone of the Kosov 2 section. a – PŠ 3902b, central part of large rhabdosome, for complete counterpart see Text-fig. 7a, sample K2/10; b – PŠ 3886/2, deformed rhabdosome from sample K2/9. Both specimens × 5, scale bar 2 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4586659/files/figure.png" .

